data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home bursting with character and modern updates. Step inside to discover the high ceilings and natural light that creates an airy and spacious feel throughout. The kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinet space, perfect for storage and organization, complemented by beautiful hickory flooring that adds a touch of elegance to the space. The updated bathroom adds a touch of luxury, while the 3 season porch offers a tranquil retreat. Outside, a large fenced yard and shed with electrical provide endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. Additionally, the laundry room features a full bath complete with a relaxing jetted tub. Don't miss the chance to make this delightful property your new home sweet home!
